{
  "info": {
    "name": "EfaStream API",
    "description": "Streaming platform backend (Netflix-like).\n\n**Sample credentials:**\n- Admin: email `admin@efastream.com`, password `Admin@123`\n- User: register via Auth → Register, then login with that email/password\n- Partner: create via Admin → Create partner (e.g. email `partner@studio.com`, password `Partner@123`), then login\n\n**Sample data in requests:**\n- Register: `user@example.com` / `Password123` / John / Doe\n- Payment: `planId: 1`, `amount: 9.99`, `currency: USD`, `returnUrl`/`cancelUrl`\n- Partner create: `partner@studio.com`, `Partner@123`, company `Studio X`, contact `Jane`, phone `+1234567890`\n- Content (partner): `title`, `description`, `thumbnail`, `videoUrl`, `contentType`: MOVIE | MUSIC_VIDEO | MUSIC_AUDIO\n- Plan create: `name` (e.g. Monthly), `price` (e.g. 9.99), `durationDays` (e.g. 30)\n- Hero: `title`, `subtitle`, `imageUrl`, `link`, `active: true`\n- Verify payment: use `token` from Create payment response (e.g. `stripe_mock_1` for mock)\n- Verify email: use `token` from verification email link",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080/api" },
    { "key": "accessToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "refreshToken", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Password123\",\n  \"firstName\": \"John\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Doe\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (User)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.data.refreshToken || '');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.data.refreshToken || '');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@efastream.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin@123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Partner)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.data.refreshToken || '');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"partner@studio.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Partner@123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify Email",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-email?token=YOUR_VERIFICATION_TOKEN"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{refreshToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Forgot Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"userType\": \"USER\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/forgot-password"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Reset Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"RESET_TOKEN_FROM_EMAIL\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"NewPassword123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/reset-password"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "User",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get my profile",
